			<h3 ><a href="#p161576">Re: you know how...?</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=161576&amp;sid=e5d828c4e121f6a9e5fff5f994528e0c#p161576"><img src="http://thejapanesepage.com/phpbb/styles/tjp-embed/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17039&amp;sid=e5d828c4e121f6a9e5fff5f994528e0c" style="color: #00AA00;" class="username-coloured">Yudan Taiteki</a></strong> &raquo; Sun 12.06.2009 10:54 am </p>

			

			<div class="content">この&quot;you know how&quot;は「どうやって」じゃなくて、ただトピックを紹介する表現。「カメラを貸したんですね」みたい。</div>

			<div id="sig161576" class="signature">-Chris Kern</div>

		</div>

		
