				<a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=99953&amp;sid=e5d828c4e121f6a9e5fff5f994528e0c"><img src="http://thejapanesepage.com/phpbb/download/file.php?avatar=99953_1257905911.gif" width="46" height="60" alt="User avatar" /></a><br />
